7... Nd5 { This move will annoy every White player. } 8. Qa4+
{ Naturally  8.Bxc4  Nxc3  loses a piece. } 8... Nc6
{ As we said we always meet Qa4+ or Ne5 with Nc6. } 9. Bxc4 { Oops! } 9... Nb6
