1. d4 d5 2. c4 dxc4 3. Nc3 c5 4. d5 Nf6 5. e4 b5 6. e5 b4 7. exf6 bxc3 8. bxc3
Nd7 9. fxe7 Bxe7 10. Nf3 O-O 11. Bxc4
{ White just plays normal moves thinking he is winning with his extra pawn. }
11... Bf6 12. Bd2 Re8+ { Now the problems begin for White. } 13. Be2
{ Another normal looking move. Not seeing the hammer coming down. } 13... Ba6
{ and Black wins a piece. } *

[Event "?"]
